104
00:06:45,940 --> 00:06:51,520
And in much of Eastern Europe, the former Soviet Union,

105
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:55,910
the collapse was according to kind of national or ethnic lines,

106
00:06:55,910 --> 00:06:59,670
as people reclaimed a sense of their past

107
00:06:59,670 --> 00:07:02,870
and what they considered to be somehow their authentic history

108
00:07:02,870 --> 00:07:04,930
and their authentic culture.

109
00:07:04,930 --> 00:07:10,460
