130
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:34,210
There are others, intellectuals, who think very highly of him

131
00:08:34,210 --> 00:08:39,409
and who, in my view, tend to romanticize many of his contributions

132
00:08:39,409 --> 00:08:43,450
