00:09:21,970 --> 00:09:24,690
And he was the one who had made Anyuan famous.

143
00:09:24,690 --> 00:09:28,830
And you can buy Mao paraphernalia all over the place.

144
00:09:28,830 --> 00:09:36,050
And I heard nothing but warm feelings for him on the part of poor people

145
00:09:36,050 --> 00:09:40,000
and on the part of quite well-off people alike.

146
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:43,300
But I also spend a lot of time in the cities of China

147
00:09:43,300 --> 00:09:45,740
and on university campuses in China.

148
00:09:45,740 --> 00:09:50,390
And there, you often find very, very different images of him.

149
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:53,740
So it's a very complicated legacy.

150
00:09:53,740 --> 00:09:58,560
But I think it's a legacy that it's impossible for the current leadership

151
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:00,910
